{"data":[{"id":564327525,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b9c70844f960b967c2751063b6484e33","url_token":"xiao-wan-wan-47-50","name":"小弯弯","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b9c70844f960b967c2751063b6484e33","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564327525","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546353388,"updated_time":1546353388,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"comment_count":15,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e偏一下题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想后\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明（以下以ZM代替）不出大众所料地失败了。目前势如破竹的打趣，讥讽，阴谋论，这些都是可以预见的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想换个视角，抱着客观的心态，\u003cb\u003e在其是一名真的想证明哥德巴赫猜想的高中生的设定下\u003c/b\u003e，试图情景还原，并说说自己看法。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e某天数学课外班，一位老师正在科普数学里的几大猜想。“这些猜想极具挑战性，想证明....”老师摸了摸自己后脑勺的发际线，轻叹了口气，“....太难太难了。”他却没发觉，除了暗笑他闪亮秃头的学生外，还有一位眼中闪过了异样的亮光。（不是秃头的反光）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e于是乎，ZM诞生了。“这是历史性的一刻，”ZM心中充斥着每个人年轻时都曾有过的轻狂和中二，“我有很强的冲劲，我有一点点天赋，我相信人定胜天！”ZM望向了百度上自己小公鸡决定下来的哥德巴赫猜想，一眼千年，望到未来人对自己的敬仰，看见过去哥德巴赫对自己的微笑，不禁咧起了嘴开始傻笑。无独有偶，这时ZM突然看见了一张黑猴的照片，笑得也是这么开心，心中一乐，头像就有了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哪怕写六张纸的“一”也是很耗时间的。这对ZM来说，耗费了他数月的时间--网上买书，自学，头脑风暴，哪怕即将到来的高考压力也只得抛之脑后--\u003cb\u003e他把大部分精力都投进来了。\u003c/b\u003e终于，灵感出现了，他兴奋，他雀跃，晚上完全没有心思睡觉，而是在被窝中无限遐想....\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“不如在知乎吧，b格高一点。时间就1.1吧，当新年冲天炮！”他为自己聪明的点子感到暗喜--毕竟我可是证明了哥德巴赫猜想的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e故事开始了转折，这一转，便没了回升。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e讥讽，嘲笑，玩梗...虽然这种声音层出不穷，但依然有一小部分人在期待奇迹--虽然在他眼里是已经尘埃落定的事实。这些并不会有实质性的影响，虽然他那时的确处在了民科的范畴。“等1.1就能看好戏咯。”他甚至一度产生了这样的想法。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e01/01/2019，一个ZM一辈子也不会忘记的日子。当别的同龄人正享受着自己的时光，他正在经历煎熬。那些质疑声，变成了否定；那些否定，变成了谩骂。他将来会很难度过这道坎，因为他始终不明白自己的努力为何换来了恶意。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上是我\u003cb\u003e在其是一名真的想证明哥德巴赫猜想的高中生的设定下\u003c/b\u003e，进行的脑补。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e请各位看客会想一下自己的高中生涯。真正有和主人公一样数学热情的人有几个？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果他给他的老师去看这篇的论文，有师德的老师会微笑的指出错误，然后进行鼓励。在知乎，鼓励的人有，但\u003cb\u003e极少。\u003c/b\u003e绝大部分人是在泼冷水，恶意猜测。汉隆剃刀告诉我们：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e如果问题本质可以用一个词：愚蠢  来解释，则在思考问题本质时勿恶意猜测。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很明显，结果证明在知乎如果真有人想骗粉是有难度的。（至少不会用这种方式）既然问题本质仅仅因为“愚蠢”，则ZM不应被口诛笔伐成这样。他展现出了同龄人不多见的勇气，努力，哪怕只有一点点的天赋，和对数学的热情，若只是因为年少轻狂而应得此下场......\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e累，自闭了\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"偏一下题\u003cb\u003e高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想后\u003c/b\u003e 证明（以下以ZM代替）不出大众所料地失败了。目前势如破竹的打趣，讥讽，阴谋论，这些都是可以预见的。我想换个视角，抱着客观的心态，\u003cb\u003e在其是一名真的想证明哥德巴赫猜想的高中生的设定下\u003c/b\u003e，试图情景还原，并说说自己看法…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=209\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=207\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","totals":489}}
